title: After The Storm (feat. Tyler, The Creator & Bootsy Collins)

lastfm.summary: "After the Storm" was released on January 12th, 2018. The song features Bootsy Collins and Tyler, the Creator. The music video released to accompany the song features pastel colors and a large focus on flowers and gardens, possibly inspired by Tyler, the Creator's 2017 album, Flower Boy. Read more on Last.fm.
